<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM6.10.3">
<l>pūṇā taṉalun taṟukaṇ vēḻam maṟuka vaḷaimaruppaip</l>
<l>pēṇāṉ vāṅki yamutaṅ koṇṭa perumāṉ tirumārvaṉ</l>
<l>pāṇā vaṇṭu muraluṅ kūnta lāycci tayirveṇṇey</l>
<l>nāṇā tuṇṭāṉ nāmañ collil namōnā rāyaṇamē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>If you say the name of the one who, without shame, ate the ghee [and] curds</l>
<l>Of the herdess with tresses where bees musically hum,</l>
<l rend="indent">the one with Tiru at his chest,</l>
<l>The great lord who brought nectar, the one without concern,</l>
<l rend="indent">having seized a curved tusk,</l>
<l>To crush the elephant without fetters with bulging eyes</l>
<l rend="indent">which burned [angrily], [that itself is] the Namō Nārāyaṇam.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
